Assignment-2
~~~~~~~~~~~~
1. How to display images in title bar?
Answer: By providing a favicon.


2. What is the purpose of "alt" attribute of img tag?
Answer: The alt attribute of image tag is to display and alternate text for the image when the image is unable to display.

3. Create the following web pages using html tags:
		a. Home Page
		b. Employees Page
		c.  Depts Page
		d.  Contact Us Page
		e.   About Us Page
		
Hints:
		-->   Home page should provide hyperlinks to  all Other web pages
		-->   Employees Page display employee details in table format. 
					Columns:  Empno, Ename, Job, Sal, Deptno
		-->  Dept names display using list tags : ol/ul
		-->  Contact Page display contact details. Provide external hyperlinks to facebook, youtube, twitter, etc...
		-->  About us page uses :  p tag, img tags
